        "questionParts": [
          "Let \\(f(x, y) = x^2 - y^2\\).",
          "At the point \\((1, 1)\\), consider the direction vector \\(\\mathbf{v} = \\langle 1, 2 \\rangle\\).",
          "Compute the directional derivative \\(D_{\\mathbf{v}}f(1,1)\\)."
